To use Camera witrh Raspberry pi-5, open the terminal by pressing Ctrl+Alt+T,
then use the following commnads.

1. To test the Camera
	$libcamera-hello

2.	To capture image
	$libcamera-jpeg -o Test.jpeg

3.	To capture video [The following command will capture the video for 10 seconds in mp4 format]
	$libcamera-vid -t 10s -o Test.mp4

Note:
	a]	The $ symbol in every command indicats the command prompt and is 
		not hte part of the command. hence you nbeed to type the
		command by ommiting the $ symbol
	b]	The images / Videos are stored in the current directory open 
		in the command prompt
